graph TD
    Start["Update Loop Time"] --> P1["1. Timers<br/>Execute expired timer callbacks"]
    P1 --> P2["2. Pending Callbacks<br/>Deferred I/O callbacks"]
    P2 --> P3["3. Idle / Prepare<br/>Internal housekeeping"]
    P3 --> P4["4. Poll for I/O<br/>Block for events via<br/>epoll / kqueue / IOCP"]
    P4 --> P5["5. Check Callbacks<br/>setImmediate in Node.js"]
    P5 --> P6["6. Close Callbacks<br/>Handle cleanup via uv_close"]
    P6 --> Alive{"Active handles<br/>or requests?"}
    Alive -->|Yes| Start
    Alive -->|No| Exit["Exit Loop"]
